类 AppBlockingPackageInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.content.pm.AppBlockingPackageInfo

  • public final class AppBlockingPackageInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Parcelable to hold information on app blocking allowlist or denylist for a package.

    • 字段详细资料

      • packageName

        public final java.lang.String packageName
        Package name for the package to block or allow.

      • FLAG_SYSTEM_APP

        public static final int FLAG_SYSTEM_APP
        Represents system app which does not need #signature.
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • FLAG_WHOLE_ACTIVITY

        public static final int FLAG_WHOLE_ACTIVITY
        Denylist or allowlist every Activities in the package. When this is set, activities may be null.
        另请参阅:
        常量字段值

      • flags

        public final int flags
        flags to give additional information on the package.
        另请参阅:
        FLAG_SYSTEM_APP, FLAG_WHOLE_ACTIVITY

      • minRevisionCode

        public final int minRevisionCode
        Package version should be bigger than this to block or allow. (package version > minRevisionCode) 0 means do not care min version.

      • maxRevisionCode

        public final int maxRevisionCode
        Package version should be smaller than this to block or allow. (package version < minRevisionCode) 0 means do not care max version.

      • signatures

        public final Signature[] signatures
        Signature of package. This can be null if target package is from system so that package name is enough to uniquely identify it (= flags having FLAG_SYSTEM_APP. Matching any member of array is considered as matching package.

      • activities

        public final java.lang.String[] activities
        List of activities (full class name). This can be null if Activity is not blocked or allowed. Additionally, FLAG_WHOLE_ACTIVITY set in flags shall have null for this.

      • CREATOR

        public static final <any> CREATOR

    • 构造器详细资料
